<h2 class="bold font-l">Puyo Puyo 2</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Satan disguises himself by wearing a simple mask and changing his name to Masked Satan. Arle has no problem seeing through his poor disguise. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PaperThinDisguise" class='trope-example-link'>Paper-Thin Disguise</a></p>
</div>
